<item>
            <title>[CXF-2210] Change Jsr250BeanPostProcessor bean defination in cxf.xml</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CXF-2210</link>
                <project id="12310511" key="CXF">CXF</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Can the Jsr250BeanPostProcessor def please be changed to :&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;bean id=&quot;org.apache.cxf.bus.spring.Jsr250BeanPostProcessor&quot; class=&quot;org.apache.cxf.bus.spring.Jsr250BeanPostProcessor&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
     &amp;lt;property name=&quot;bus&quot; ref=&quot;cxf&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;/bean&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Using @Resource with a PostBeanProcessor causes FactoryBeans to create their bean before all PostProcessorBeans are created.&lt;br/&gt;
E.g. JndiObjectFactoryBean, a lookup is forced because spring wants to find all the beans that match the Bus interface. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
